{
  "stem": "25651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brother was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he immediately became a doctor in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] And that's, in fact, how my brother Leo saved my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But that's a different story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Is it an appropriate place to tell me now?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I need to tell you how we arrived, because I told you how [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Melosh ?] was supplanted by me as the youngest child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his problem was that he was jealous of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, he was a very loving boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had a problem because-- it was his problem, not mine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was his problem that-- but as he grew older, and as we became more and more alone with my mother as the years came to 1944, our relationship as brothers strengthened, because he started working on a Jewish farm.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Livingshtine's ?] were the farmers that he worked with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as he was-- he worked, first of all, at the, at the furniture factory, to be an apprentice carpenter.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, they were afraid of employing a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he went and worked with the [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Livingshtines. ?] They were the only farmers, Jewish farmers, in the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Quite picturesque.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you plowed with horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you sowed by hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was all very primitive, but very-- it was a beautiful life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, beautiful, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] you know, women had to wash up and forever feed the cows, and feed the horses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a drudgery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But to a kid, a farm is, is terrifically exciting, and animals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Livingshtines ?] weren't kosher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had rabbits.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they ate rabbits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my relationship with [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Melosh, ?] or his problem disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He became 16.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
